e of Islam is best?\u201d Ibn Mas\u2019ud said, \u201cPrayer.\u201d The man said, \u201cThen what?\u201d Ibn Mas\u2019ud said, \u201cCharity.\u201d The man said, \u201cThen what?\u201d Ibn Mas\u2019ud said,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34603,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/11\/30\/ibn-masud-fear-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":41341,"position":3},"title":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud on Taqwa: Sinful to show anger when told to fear Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 30, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Zayd ibn Wahb reported: Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cIt is enough sin for a man to get angry when he is told to fear Allah.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r 8588 Grade: Rijal al-Sahih (narrators are reliable) according to Al-Haythami \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0632\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0647\u0652\u0628\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37353,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/11\/10\/abdullah-small-bidah\/","url_meta":{"origin":41341,"position":4},"title":"Abdullah on Bid\u2019ah: Rejection of apparently good or small innovations","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 10, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Salamah al-Hamdani reported: We used to sit by the door of Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud, may Allah b